{"tid":278974,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本四國五日四夜","createTime":"2017-06-11T00:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T17:11:15.000Z","uid":3108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd944621126ed209cbf567bf4263e5c2ca21b2a3","tid":278974,"uid":3108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"前嗰排膽粗粗見平買咗去大阪嘅機票 然後一直都冇乜理 到上個星期先醒起自己買咗機票 所以臨急臨忙走去計劃行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為時間太忟 所以上連登搵咗個巴打去四國嘅post 參考咗佢去四國嘅行程 定咗大致係去高松同埋松山 最主要係想去貓島撚下貓（我係貓奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） 然後其他時間就會搵下啲景點去<br />\n因為一條麻甩佬嘅關係 景點呢家嘢好隨心所欲 同埋亦會有好多空閒時間 所以就想上連登開post記錄低自己嘅旅程 同埋解下悶咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為聽日先飛 所以依家仲未執過行李 打算求其帶兩三套衫同埋一頂帽就算<br />\n住宿方面就book晒4晚 airbnb 合共大約一千左右 算係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後會keep 住更新 希望毒撚開post有人會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a88553e7d0e28d5874b7178168f6d0ae92d906","tid":278974,"uid":3108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/085423_55e2e83a888494ad518b3caad48236fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F085423_55e2e83a888494ad518b3caad48236fd.jpg&h=1a533226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一晚會住嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3226008f8fd91a317486b13e18009e3f3c78b764","tid":278974,"uid":74571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:56:01.000Z","msg":"巴打幾號返?<br />\n我過幾日去一個人渣車，如果夾到行程可以兜埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c39467bbd69d245a6217470bfe01202809eb0a","tid":278974,"uid":3108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"