ces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9ec59740ddc03e9311ec774284bea34f57c708","tid":278974,"uid":3108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n12號去 16號返</blockquote><br />\n咁未必夾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我14去19返</blockquote><br />\n唔緊要啦 我啲交通都大致搵過 我都係去四四國鐵路pass 任搭嗰隻<br />\n巴打自己一個自駕遊咁爽 諗住去邊忽</blockquote><br />\n暫時應該係淡路 德島 高松 小豆島<br />\n<br />\n星期日如果早起身去轉高知朝市，太遲訂果邊已經冇咩酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係早一晚過定去唔洗咁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n你放棄定都得, 高松去高知要2個鐘火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去旅行早起係一項挑戰</blockquote><br />\n可能我平時慣左4-5點就起身開工，好多時去旅行都晨咁早彈左起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n四五點就起身 巴打份工都好辛苦下喎"},{"pid":"23db255fc407db155f3b50ef8854dc0ea7f3cb9b","tid":278974,"uid":3108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/092858_00640822aa6b6c0f0b3cc039d6ea7173.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F092858_00640822aa6b6c0f0b3cc039d6ea7173.jpg&h=b0289be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n毒撚一個去呢個gip 會唔會太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ca38c465dca32de751e9d48daa173f40f933d7","tid":278974,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/092858_00640822aa6b6c0f0b3cc039d6ea7173.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F092858_